dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Waupaca County, WI 2025
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and right of ways (ROW) for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2025 and includes the layers 'WAUPACA_ROADS_2025' and 'WAUPACA_ROW_2025'. [Roads: This data represents the Waupaca County transportation network. A single line is used to represent the center of a road. All roads are geocoded with a address range.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
